c: 7
v: 167
t: "Soni (mwakumbusyani) ndema ja ŵagombelesye Ambuje ŵenu yanti; chisimu chene taŵeje ali nkwatumichisya (Ayudao) mpaka lisiku lya Kiyama ŵachaŵeje ali nkwapa ilagasyo yakusakala, chisimu Ambuje ŵenu ni Ŵachitema pakupeleka ipotesi, soni chisimu Ŵalakweo ni Ŵakululuka kusyene Ŵachanasa channope"